room_title: Escape room "1,000 Feet Down" by Paradox Challenge Rooms in Tupelo
room_description: Some of our team went down to the lowest level of the mine to do an equipment check, and the shaft commapsed!  We haven't been able to send anyone down yet, so we need you to investigate and see if there is any hope of saving them.  You'll have to be clever and quick to save them before the air runs out!
